title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported JAR file in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported JAR file for the second time.
EB: The out of sync message should not be displayed when overwriting the exported JAR file for the second time.
SR:
1. Open a directory (project)
2. Export the directory
3. Place the exported JAR file in the same directory
4. Overwrite the exported JAR file
5. Repeat step 4 for the second time
